sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as End User
    participant GW as Ingress Gateway
    participant Web as Web Pod (v1/Stable)
    participant API as API Pod (Canary/v2)
    participant AuthZ as AuthZ Check
    participant Egress as Egress Gateway
    participant Provider as External Gateway
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Client->>GW: GET /checkout (HTTPS)
    GW->>GW: Evaluates VirtualService Rules
    GW->>Web: Route 90% (mTLS handshake, SPIFFE validation)
    Web->>Web: Processes request
    
    %% Gateway route to Canary
    Note over GW, API: Alternative Canary Route (10%)
    GW->>API: Route 10% (mTLS handshake)
    
    %% Authorization Policy
    API->>AuthZ: Evaluates AuthorizationPolicy rules
    alt Authorization Success
        AuthZ-->>API: Allowed
    else Authorization Denied
        AuthZ-->>API: HTTP 403 Forbidden (Halt)
    end
    
    %% Egress gateway call
    API->>Egress: Outbound request to api.stripe.com
    Egress->>Provider: Forwards request with SNI verification
    Provider-->>Egress: HTTP 200 OK
    Egress-->>API: Delivers checkout session token
    
    API-->>GW: Returns checkout success response
    GW-->>Client: Returns JSON response
    
    %% Telemetry async
    Note over Web, Prom: Telemetry collection
    Web-->>Prom: Envoy scrapes metrics (latency, HTTP codes)
    API-->>Prom: Envoy scrapes metrics (latency, HTTP codes)
